Code written by Jon Harder at Greatmoods ltd
2012

Connect.php used as a connection object to access database
$conn = new Connection(); // will create an object and automatically connect to default database


make a query to database via make_query($query); method
$conn->make_query($query); // makes a query to database and stores result in private result feild
			   // get the result through get accessor
$result = $conn->get_result();

